        "🇻🇦 <strong>Vulgata:</strong> Nabuchodonosor rex omnibus populis gentibus et linguis qui habitant in universa terra pax vobis multiplicetur<br><hr style='border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);'><br>",
        "<strong><span style='color: #d4af37;'>ESTUDO LEXICAL:</span></strong> <em>שְׁלָמְכוֹן</em> – 'Paz' – paz, bem-estar. <em>יִשְׂגֵּא</em> – 'multiplicada' – multiplicar, aumentar.<br><hr style='border: 1px solid rgba(212, 175, 55, 0.2);'><br>",
